        <mxCell id="V6klS_5CtcvHBXw9OeqT-2" value="JavaScript from example.com could be trying to fetch from other domains. If those other domains don&#39;t trust example.com they won&#39;t allow it as an origin." style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;rounded=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
